$timescale 1ns $end
$comment
  MDIO (IEEE 802.3 Clause 22 + Clause 45) Pro decoder
  happy-path fixture. Sequence:
    1. 32-cycle preamble
    2. C22 R  PHY 0x01 reg 0x02 → 0x55AA
    3. C22 W  PHY 0x01 reg 0x10 = 0xABCD
    4. C45 ADDR  port 0x03 devad 0x1F = 0x1234
    5. C45 R     port 0x03 devad 0x1F → 0xCAFE
    6. C45 W     port 0x03 devad 0x1F = 0xBABE
  Regenerate via: dart run tool/generate_mdio_fixture.dart
$end
$scope module tb $end
$var wire 1 ! MDC $end
$var wire 1 " MDIO $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
$dumpvars
0!
1"
$end
